headline: Truist Financial Maintains Buy Rating on Dick’s Sporting Goods (DKS)
summary: On May 20, Truist Financial analyst Joseph Civello maintained a Buy rating on DICK’S Sporting Goods, Inc. (NYSE:DKS), with a $245.00 price target. The rating came after DICK’S Sporting Goods, Inc. (NYSE:DKS) announced its preliminary Q1 2025 results and plans to acquire Foot Locker (NYSE:FL) on May 15.
